Meyer Bergman and Hoopp Buy 2 Czech Malls for EU300 Million

-- B y   R o s s   L a r s e n
-- 
2011-09-30T08:50:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/meyer-bergman-and-hoopp-buy-2-czech-malls-for-eu300-million.html
Meyer Bergman and Healthcare of
Ontario  Pension Plan  purchased two shopping malls in the  Czech
Republic  for 300 million euros. The malls are Forum Nova
Karolina in Ostrava and Forum Usti nad Labem.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ross Larsen in London at 
